\"code\":-5000,\"msg\":\"Path /fapi/v1/positionRisk, Method GET is invalid\"}\n\n5. 测试市场价格...\n🔗 请求: GET https://testnet.binancefuture.com/fapi/v1/ticker/price\n📋 参数: {'symbol': 'BTCUSDT', 'timestamp': 1773004177980, 'signature': 'a3b4f0fceeb570004ae613a792595821c9c62e21a0b08e7d199b99b577861561'}\n📡 响应状态: 200\n✅ 请求成功: {\n  \"symbol\": \"BTCUSDT\",\n  \"price\": \"67014.20\",\n  \"time\": 1773004171771\n}...\n✅ BTC当前价格: 67014.2 USDT\n\n==================================================\n🎉 币安测试网连接验证完成!\n✅ API连接正常\n✅ 账户信息可获取\n✅ 市场数据正常\n✅ 准备开始交易!"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":475,"aggregated":"🚀 虞姬币安测试网连接验证启动\n⏰ 时间: 2026-03-09 05:09:37\n🧪 开始测试币安测试网连接...\n--------------------------------------------------\n\n1. 测试服务器时间...\n🔗 请求: GET https://testnet.binancefuture.com/fapi/v1/time\n📋 参数: {'timestamp': 1773004177667, 'signature': 'c40108baa19d928dc80269663c92db720db8161001a5e27d107168dbd99b9d48'}\n📡 响应状态: 200\n✅ 请求成功: {\n  \"serverTime\": 1773004177704\n}...\n✅ 服务器时间: 2026-03-09 05:09:37.704000\n\n2. 测试交易对信息...\n🔗 请求: GET https://testnet.binancefuture.com/fapi/v1/exchangeInfo\n📋 参数: {'timestamp': 1773004177732, 'signature': 'cc20b86bb49614657c5dfa0c24c927c2375b2124ba925deebe28b05f1b55d76f'}\n📡 响应状态: 200\n✅ 请求成功: {\n  \"timezone\": \"UTC\",\n  \"serverTime\": 1772685584858,\n  \"futuresType\": \"U_MARGINED\",\n  \"rateLimits\": [\n    {\n      \"rateLimitType\": \"REQUEST_WEIGHT\",\n      \"interval\": \"MINUTE\",\n      \"intervalNum\": 1,\n      \"limit\": 6000\n    },\n    {\n      \"rateLimitType\": \"ORDERS\",\n      \"interval\": \"MINUTE\",\n      \"intervalNum\": 1,\n      \"limit\": 1200\n    },\n    {\n      \"rateLimitType\": \"ORDERS\",\n      \"interval\": \"SECOND\",\n      \"intervalNum\": 10,\n      \"limit\": 300\n    }\n  ],\n  \"exchangeFilters\": [],\n  \"ass...\n✅ BTCUSDT交易对信息获取成功\n\n3. 测试账户信息...\n🔗 请求: GET https://testnet.binancefuture.com/fapi/v1/account\n📋 参数: {'timestamp': 1773004177858, 'signature': '4f19fe3d7dceae65b9