d cycles and four advanced strategies\n- **OKX demo environment**: Switched to OKX simulation trading when real API authentication failed\n- **BTC price integration**: Used OKX public API for real-time market data while maintaining simulated trading\n- **Alternative password testing**: Tested Qlzwqc2012. password but authentication still failed with HTTP 401\n- **Demo account transition**: Successfully connected to OKX demo API (9173aacb-75b5-4377-b682-2835afb8be6f) for real simulated trading\n- **High leverage focus**: Implemented 10U starting capital system with 10-25x leverage and high win rates (75-90%)\n\n## Open TODOs\n- Fix OKX private API connection (401 authentication errors - passphrase incorrect)\n- Successfully execute one of the trading systems (all attempts terminated via SIGTERM)\n- Monitor system performance and trading results\n- Achieve progress toward $1M target from initial $100 capital\n- Implement real-time reporting and optimization\n- Connect to OKX demo trading environment successfully\n- Validate OKX passphrase and API configuration\n- Continue running OKX demo trading systems (nova-pine, tide-basil sessions)\n- Monitor high leverage contract trading with 10U starting capital\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- Must use QQ platform formatting for media (<qqimg>, <qqvoice>, <qqfile>, <qqvideo> tags)\n- No TTS/STT capabilities configured\n- Systems must run 7*24 hours continuously\n- Trading simulation uses BTC as base asset with simulated price volatility\n- Must check SOUL.md, USER.md, memory files before each session\n- Must embed media using specific QQ tags: <qqimg>URL</qqimg>, <qqvoice>path</qqvoice>, <qqfile>path/URL</qqfile>, <qqvideo>path/URL</qqvideo>\n- Cannot send images without embedding in text response\n- Cannot use tool calls without accompanying text response\n- TTS plugin not configured (cannot generate speech automatically)\n- STT not configured (cannot transcribe user voice messages)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- Execute trading syste